name: Cytotoxicity, Errant Stigma, Dispersal Method Resulting in Necrosis of Host
name_original: Cytotoxicity, Errant Stigma, Dispersal Method Resulting in Necrosis of Host
description:
Your house is dying. The world is vicious. You need to find somewhere else to live.

This is a shortish interactive story with twelve endings, published September 2021.
